{"tid":1707243,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭就係要流血 要打","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:58:28.000Z","uid":162713,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4244eb346b7dd2b67172e544abb86ea32715a5ed","tid":1707243,"uid":162713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"頭先行緊返屋企<br />\n聽到隔離個阿叔係度大大聲<br />\n本身聽佢講野都似藍絲廢中<br />\n正想屌鳩佢<br />\n但佢講嘅野又有少少道理<br />\n搞到我一時唔記得屌佢<br />\n<br />\n阿叔：咩和理非晒氣啦！依家又話抗爭，要係政府手上攞野，用把口就攞到，邊度都無呢個道理！抗爭就係無啱唔啱，就係要打，一直打，打到贏為止！<br />\n<br />\n聽落好似有道理，但又好似唔係咁啱，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"9ffc89548f182ba88a7b63657a9c92569333ae9d","tid":1707243,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"根本係正常，和理非無問題，問題係以為只靠和理非就得個班，叫左膠<br />\n<br />\n我一向叫文同武，有D人勁當然可以文武雙全"},{"pid":"6612f15f7d7e18f81ff5c3889aae488b65af22f9","tid":1707243,"uid":91929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:52:40.000Z","msg":"出文未"},{"pid":"be1de236fa22037634d527867507efa495dfbbcb","tid":1707243,"uid":162713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6612f15f7d7e18f81ff5c3889aae488b65af22f9","tid":1707243,"uid":91929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:52:40.000Z","msg":"出文未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"原來係手財奴巴打<br />\n好多謝你仲記得我篇頹作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}